<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="R" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Refuge1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Refuge,</orth> subst. 1) protection from danger, expedient in distress: <bibl n="shak. r2 2.2.135" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 II, 2, 135</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 2.2.25" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A II, 2, 25</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.4.69" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 4, 69</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 3.3.11" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. III, 3, 11</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 5.3.11" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. V, 3, 11</bibl>.<lb />2) specious excuse, subterfuge: <cit><quote>at the least this r. let me find,</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 1654" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 1654</bibl></cit>.
